{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778982860148,"sessionID":"ses_1cc5be10bffeihXrzY1FV2TH0l","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_1mCzqwx43L7VrbFgPWLgi2lA","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":400},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"Please provide as much information as you can: \\n\\n* **Suggested term label:Ferritin-specific autophagy**\\n\\n\\n* **Definition (A ferritin-specific autophagic pathway leading to the release of the iron stored inside ferritin.)**\\n\\n\\n* **Reference, in format PMID:38714719, 25327288, 26436293**\\n(REQUIRED)\\n\\n* **Gene product name and ID to be annotated to this term: FTH1, NCOA4**\\n\\n\\n* **Parent term(s): GO:0006914 - Autophagy**\\n\\n\\n* **Children terms (if applicable)** Should any existing terms that should be moved underneath this new proposed term?\\n\\n\\n* **Synonyms (ferritinophagy - exact)**\\n\\n* **Cross-references**\\n* For enzymes, please provide RHEA and/or EC numbers. \\n* Can also provide MetaCyc, KEGG, Wikipedia, and other links.\\n\\n* **Any other information**\\n\",\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws7grbwP\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"ValWood\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"Adding with parent \\\"macroautophagy\\\"\\nand as ferritinophagy\\nexact synonym ferritin-specific autophagy\\n\\nstandardized def\\nThe selective degradation of ferritin to release iron by macroautophagy. \\n\\n\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-01-19T17:29:56Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n16:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/30894#issuecomment-3769482255\",\n17:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n18:     },\n19:     {\n20:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAv1-tA\",\n21:       \"author\": {\n22:         \"login\": \"ValWood\"\n23:       },\n24:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n25:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent  please add this term\",\n26:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-29T15:24:56Z\",\n27:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n28:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n29:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n30:       \"reactionGroups\": [\n31:         {\n32:           \"content\": \"EYES\",\n33:           \"users\": {\n34:             \"totalCount\": 1\n35:           }\n36:         }\n37:       ],\n38:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/30894#issuecomment-4345134772\",\n39:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n40:     },\n41:     {\n42:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAv2PvQ\",\n43:       \"author\": {\n44:         \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n45:       },\n46:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n47:       \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/25117814462)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n48:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-29T15:25:27Z\",\n49:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n50:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n51:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n52:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n53:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/30894#issuecomment-4345139133\",\n54:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n55:     }\n56:   ],\n57:   \"title\": \"NTR: [Ferritin-specific autophagy]\",\n58:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/30894\"\n59: }\n\n(End of file - total 59 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"Please provide as much information as you can: \\n\\n* **Suggested term label:Ferritin-specific autophagy**\\n\\n\\n* **Definition (A ferritin-specific autophagic pathway leading to the release of the iron stored inside ferritin.)**\\n\\n\\n* **Reference, in format PMID:38714719, 25327288, 26436293**\\n(REQUIRED)\\n\\n* **Gene product name and ID to be annotated to this term: FTH1, NCOA4**\\n\\n\\n* **Parent term(s): GO:0006914 - Autophagy**\\n\\n\\n* **Children terms (if applicable)** Should any existing terms that should be moved underneath this new proposed term?\\n\\n\\n* **Synonyms (ferritinophagy - exact)**\\n\\n* **Cross-references**\\n* For enzymes, please provide RHEA and/or EC numbers. \\n* Can also provide MetaCyc, KEGG, Wikipedia, and other links.\\n\\n* **Any other information**\\n\",\n  \"comments\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws7grbwP\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"ValWood\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"Adding with parent \\\"macroautophagy\\\"\\nand as ferritinophagy\\nexact synonym ferritin-specific autophagy\\n\\nstandardized def\\nThe selective degradation of ferritin to release iron by macroautophagy. \\n\\n\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-01-19T17:29:56Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/30894#issuecomment-3769482255\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABAv1-tA\",","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"__issue_context__.json","time":{"start":1778982860084,"end":1778982860144}},"id":"prt_e33a43526001pg6pRSNf1fa6bZ","sessionID":"ses_1cc5be10bffeihXrzY1FV2TH0l","messageID":"msg_e33a4202f001BOV88LJwPrJn3f"}}
