{"type":"text","timestamp":1778982885132,"sessionID":"ses_1cc5be10bffeihXrzY1FV2TH0l","part":{"id":"prt_e33a47bdb001VKhYxGG5noiCvR","messageID":"msg_e33a46733001Usk0P6g89SGEQQ","sessionID":"ses_1cc5be10bffeihXrzY1FV2TH0l","type":"text","text":"I found strong precedent: several cargo-specific macroautophagy terms use the simple pattern “The selective degradation of X by macroautophagy.” I’m validating the current ontology state and pulling the cited ferritinophagy papers now so the new term can follow that existing pattern cleanly.","time":{"start":1778982878171,"end":1778982885117}}}
